PrairieTest Auto-Reserve monitors exam slot availability on PrairieTest and alerts you when a better option opens up. No more manual refreshing.
Set your preferences and let the extension do the watching. When a preferred slot is found, you'll be notified and can confirm the reservation yourself. Nothing changes without your approval.
Key Features:

- Customizable auto-refresh intervals
- Filter by exam type (quiz, midterm, final)
- Preferred days and times selection
- Keyword filtering (e.g., location, format)
- Overlap detection with other exams
- Monitor multiple courses
- Sound alerts and browser notifications

Compatible with us.prairietest.com and ca.prairietest.com. Just keep a PrairieTest tab open and let it run.
